description: The MSCI United Kingdom IMI Low Carbon SRI Selection Capped Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large, mid- and small cap companies from the UK with high ESG characteristics and low carbon exposures, relative to their peers Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI UK ESG UCITS ETF 1D
